07:18.360 --> 07:19.300
You can't be here.

07:20.510 --> 07:21.300
Do you understand?

07:23.320 --> 07:24.180
Where can I be then?

07:27.340 --> 07:27.930
You live here?

07:28.840 --> 07:29.500
My dad–

07:30.210 --> 07:31.020
My family…

07:31.770 --> 07:32.310
I'm just...

07:33.080 --> 07:33.970
Looking after it.

07:37.860 --> 07:38.390
Thanks.

07:39.420 --> 07:40.070
It’s fine.

07:44.710 --> 07:45.550
So...

07:46.600 --> 07:48.730
What’s the name of this town?

07:49.380 --> 07:51.820
Saint-Léger-en-Charnie.

07:52.030 --> 07:54.780
Saint-Léger-en… Rahgie…

07:54.920 --> 07:56.660
That last word
didn’t even–

07:57.260 --> 07:58.170
Wasn’t even close.

07:58.280 --> 08:03.750
Saint-Léger-en-Charnie.

08:05.640 --> 08:06.150
Yap. Pretty good.

08:06.680 --> 08:07.540
En Charnie…

08:07.740 --> 08:10.450
Yeah, without the
neck, but yeah.

08:10.830 --> 08:11.560
En Charnie.

08:11.590 --> 08:13.450
I’m really bad
at French.

08:13.910 --> 08:14.240
Yeah.

08:16.850 --> 08:18.680
[chatter, glasses clinking,
music on radio]

08:24.240 --> 08:25.890
So where are you
staying tonight?

08:28.920 --> 08:29.590
I don’t know.

08:36.890 --> 08:37.530
Let’s walk.

08:38.200 --> 08:38.650
Why?

08:44.795 --> 08:46.421
[car boot closing]

08:47.330 --> 08:48.290
Yeah, that way.

08:56.700 --> 08:57.560
Oh god!

08:59.490 --> 09:00.090
Jesus.

09:02.050 --> 09:04.180
