make something up.

13:45.550 --> 13:46.340
I...

13:47.600 --> 13:48.880
I came here
with someone.

13:50.630 --> 13:51.620
Then they dumped me.

13:53.100 --> 13:56.060
I’ve been trying to hitchhike
back to Paris since.

13:56.200 --> 13:57.810
How come you’re struggling?

13:59.470 --> 14:00.700
