that.

14:01.720 --> 14:03.640
I wasn’t struggling
for offers.

14:05.240 --> 14:05.800
Just...

14:06.300 --> 14:08.320
Ones that were
worth taking.

14:09.900 --> 14:12.030
What do you wanna
do tonight?

14:13.450 --> 14:14.820
I’ve bought a lot of wine.

14:16.380 --> 14:16.890
Jeez.

14:18.450 --> 14:19.290
