14:24.250 --> 14:25.960
Nothing else to do.

14:27.020 --> 14:28.930
There’s plenty left to do.

14:29.990 --> 14:30.480
Yeah?

14:32.010 --> 14:33.760
What did you do before?

14:34.840 --> 14:37.180
You really don’t do
anything, do you.

14:39.020 --> 14:40.090
What would you do?

14:40.220 --> 14:42.420
I don’t live in a
fuck off house, do I?

14:44.920 --> 14:46.820
What did you do
back home?

14:47.850 --> 14:48.920
I sing mostly.

14:49.240 --> 14:49.990
And I...

14:50.980 --> 14:53.350
I wrote my songs.

14:55.170 --> 14:56.830
Singer, songwriter.

14:57.160 --> 14:57.880
Player.

14:59.710 --> 14:59.970
