[footsteps]

17:05.240 --> 17:06.369
I tried calling!

17:06.420 --> 17:07.290
Hey!

17:13.890 --> 17:14.829
Shall we…

17:15.300 --> 17:15.760
Where?

17:15.859 --> 17:16.900
Just this way.

17:29.030 --> 17:30.140
Just you and mom here?

17:30.730 --> 17:31.860
Mh-hm.

17:49.830 --> 17:51.410
Fucking hell.

17:52.480 --> 17:53.180
Who’s that?

17:55.250 --> 17:57.850
That’s my fiancé,
Charlie.

17:59.470 --> 18:00.590
You’re engaged?

18:02.260 --> 18:03.010
Mh-hm.

18:07.940 --> 18:08.610
